{"tid":1727370,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"11月24日 星期日 區議會選舉投票日 07:30 - 22:30","createTime":"2019-11-16T12:02:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"648f89aaea80f0b31997d9fadb8196c6a0317d75","tid":1727370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"11月24日 星期日 區議會選舉投票日 07:30 - 22:30<br />\n<br />\n記得去投票<br />\n<br />\n2019年區議會一般選舉將於11月24日舉行，所有合資格在是次選舉中投票的選民應已收到投票通知卡。選民請帶備香港身分證正本或指定的替代文件前往投票通知卡上列明的指定投票站投票。尚未收到投票通知卡的選民，請登入「選民資料網上查閱系統」(<a href=\"http://www.voterinfo.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterinfo.gov.hk&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=586f2982\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.voterinfo.gov.hk</a>)或致電2891 1001查詢選民身分及獲編配的投票站詳情（如適用）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.elections.gov.hk%2Fdc2019%2Fchi%2Findex.html&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=224a0f24\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.elections.gov.hk/dc2019/chi/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"fc3d7c0ffb060bfc29da17a35985539a145d6b08","tid":1727370,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:10:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0678436cdb37948e854f26f8ca958f58f4bf2f51","tid":1727370,"uid":29355,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T02:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ec3gTde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEc3gTde.png&h=6d23acc0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93c723145a879c8072aceb9a62cfdc839641bb7a","tid":1727370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T09:05:43.000Z","msg":"星期日"},{"pid":"874117676d87246b3d6fd787ab4356505a123f69","tid":1727370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T15:41:37.000Z","msg":"推"},