記，以便準時開始。<br />\n -  會場內，除大會攝影師外，不得拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n大會開始前一小時(下午4時至5時)亦有招收會員活動。請各會員及有意者撥冗出席。如有任何查詢，請透過telegram (@HKFUnion)或面書與工會成員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n請準會員預先填寫入會表格：<br />\n中: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FJRRvX5t488CyQVPYA&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=011ebe07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/JRRvX5t488CyQVPYA</a><br />\neng: <a href=\"https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FBmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=79179570\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/BmdiqkhX5pBEgZDy5</a><br />\n<br />\n工會Facebook：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKFUnion%2F&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=66d9319f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKFUnion/</a><br />\n工會Telegram channel：<a href=\"https://t.me/HKFIEGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKFIEGU&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQIPST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=651c1491\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKFIEGU</a><br />\n<br />\n#特別會員大會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWxRo2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWxRo2R.jpg&h=1a7a9910&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f4a1c3d1dc9187d6e9a1f20a68e4f133f48f9021","tid":1727370,"uid":279631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T00:55:54.000Z","msg":"推 !<br />\n另外，請入黎睇睇 :<br />\n今次區選已經變易等同公投, 港共正全力以赴過半數爭勝, 期望因此可以挾公投民意打壓運動。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1741433\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1741433</a>"},{"pid":"e35f851025a40977d0fbdbda18645535307414dc","tid":1727370,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:28:25.000Z","msg":"聽日"}]}